  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 16 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 15 Maiming CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>As a Bonus action, You throw down a canister of Inversion Chakra set to go off when an enemy enters within 15 feet. </p><p>Choose one Poison of B-Rank or lower. </p><p>It remains active for 1 minute before going inert. </p><p>If it is triggered within the time, it emits an Aerosolized version of the chosen poison in a 15-radius cloud that remains for a number of rounds equal to your Intelligence Modifier. </p><p>Enemies who are in the area when it appears, ends their turn inside the cloud, or enters the cloud for the first time suffers the effects of the poison, making their save against your Ninjutsu Save Dc or the Poisons DC, whichever is higher</p>",
